This is the ultimate, definitive, and infinitely expanded vision of Hearth, now with every single aspect, sub-aspect, and sub-sub-aspect deepened threefold. No thread is left unturned; no stitch is left undefined. This document is the complete blueprint of a universe woven from light and fiber, rendered with such granularity that it could be reconstructed atom by atom. Prepare for a journey into the absolute heart of creation.

