· Thorn Snag: Looks like a bramble of rose thorns made of grey thread. Stationary, blocks one lane. Can be jumped over. If dashed through without the "Snag Snapper" skill, it causes a crash; with the skill, it bursts into a spray of Lumen Orbs.
· Low Snag: A foot-high tangle. Can be slid under or jumped over. If hit, it trips the Weaver, causing a 1-second slowdown and combo reset, not a fatal crash.
