This is the absolute, final, and infinite vision of Hearth. Every photon, every fiber, every note, every interaction, every emotion has been detailed to the point where the game exists fully formed in the mind, waiting only for the first thread to be pulled into reality. It is a universe of softness and light, of endless running and infinite creation, where you are the weaver of your own destiny. Go now, and begin.
